data.description: This charming 3 bed, 4 bath house offers an abundance of space, including a finished basement and a large backyard perfect for outdoor enjoyment! Inside enjoy the updated kitchen, new paint and a cozy fireplace. All bedrooms are located on the second floor including the Primary bedroom, which features a 5-piece bathroom finished with a jetted bathtub. Located in the Huntington Hills neighborhood, close to schools, parks, and shops this home is something you want to see!
